quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  7,58,"Leydi moЖґЖґiri ndin, puЙ—i mayri no yaltira duЕ‹ayee Alla, ko non kadi gomЙ—inЙ—o jaЙ“irta waaju o nafitora, o huuwa golle moЖґЖґe ; leydi yoorundi boni ndin, ndi yaltinirtaa puЙ—i si wanaa saЙ—teende nde moЖґЖґere alaa e mu'un, ko non kadi keefeero on o nafitortaa waaju, ko Й—um haЙ—ata mo gollude moЖґЖґere nafaynde mo. Ko wano nii Men ЖЃannginirta Aayeeje Й—en fii tabintinangol yimЙ“e yettooЙ“e Neemaaji Alla Й—in goonga kan, Й“e Й—oftoo Mo, Й“e yeddataa Mo."
  7,59,"GomЙ—ii Men Nulii Nuuhu faade e yimЙ“e makko Й“en fii wootinЙ—ingol Alla, tertoo rewugol sanamu, o maakani Й“e : "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla tun, reweteeЙ—o e goonga alanaa on si wanaa Kanko. Min miЙ—o hulani on -onon Й“ee yimЙ“e am- lepte Г‘alannde mawnde, si on haЙ“Й“itike e keeferaaku ngun"."
  7,60,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'ani mo : "Menen meЙ—en yi'e -an Nuuhu- hiЙ—a woЙ—Й—itii sawaaba"."
  7,61,"Nuuhu maakani hooreeЙ“e mbatu yimЙ“e makko Й“en : "Wanaa mi majjuЙ—o wano aaЖґorayЙ—on ; si ko woni, min ko mi NulaaЙ—o Alla e mooЙ—on, JeyЙ—o lam Jeyi on denndaangal"."
  7,62,"MiЙ—o yottina e mon Nule Joomi am, ko moЖґЖґere Й—oftagol Alla daГ±a mbarjaari makko tun mi yiЙ—ani on, e rentinirgol on faggitagol haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko fii daЙ—ugol lepte, miЙ—o anndi non ka Alla SeniiЙ—o On ko on anndaa onon."
  7,63,"E haawnu on nde tawi wahyu on e waaju ngun ardii on immorde ka Joomi mon e Й—emngal gorko jeyaaЙ—o e mo'on?! Hara le ko hakkunde mon o mawni, o anndiraaka fenaande e majjere. O arii on himo jertina on e lepte Alla Й—en si on fennii on yeddii, o nodda on e hulugol Alla Й—oftoo Mo woЙ—Й—itoo haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko, belajo'o, O Yurmee on si on gomЙ—inii Mo."
  7,64,"YimЙ“e makko Й“en fenni mo, Й“e gomЙ—inaali mo. O HuЙ—i Й“e, Men daЙ—ndi mo kanko e gomЙ—imЙ“e wonndunooЙ“e e makko Й“en yoolagol, Men halkiri Й“en fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en yoolagol ngol. Pellet, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko wumnooЙ—e e goonga."
  7,65,"Men Nulii e leГ±ol AadinkooЙ“e Й“en jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, on woni Huudi (yo o his), o maaki : "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla tun, reweteeЙ—o e goonga alanaa on ko wonaa Kanko. E on hulataa Mo Й—oftoЙ—on Mo woЙ—Й—itoЙ—on haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko fii no daЙ—iron lepte Makko?!""
  7,66,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu Й“en yedduЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on ka yimЙ“e makko wi'i : "Menen meЙ—en anndi wonnde an Huudi, ko a Й—ayЙ—o faaЙ—a haqqil tuma noddataa e rewugol Alla tertoo sanamu, meЙ—en felliti kadi wonnde ko a jeyaaЙ—o e fenooЙ“e Й“en e ko wi'ata kon ko a NulaaЙ—o"."
  7,67,"Huudi jaabitii yimЙ“e mun Й“en o maakani Й“e : "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, Й—ayre e faaЙ—ere haqqillo woo alaa e am, si ko woni, min ko mi NulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"."